				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-V%C4%A9/H%E1%BB%93i-h%C6%B0u-l%C6%B0u-gi%E1%BA%A3n-thi/poem-W2fudiqzy7dfV32I0iyn4A">Hồi hưu lưu giản thi - 回休留柬詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-V%C4%A9/author-aP_eFMQeGWFWrGEB_-u0wA">Nguyễn Đức Vĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/Ph%E1%BA%A1t-T%E1%BB%91ng-l%E1%BB%99-b%E1%BB%91-v%C4%83n/poem-grqwKCBlZO2da-xlEa8EqQ">Phạt Tống lộ bố văn - 伐宋露布文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/author-k8EDHIxplIZZ0LYB28XrSA">Lý Thường Kiệt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/S%C3%B9ng-Nghi%C3%AAm-s%E1%BB%B1-V%C3%A2n-L%E1%BB%97i-s%C6%A1n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Bi-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-8qUHhF_jnn--sal5StRnKg">Sùng Nghiêm sự Vân Lỗi sơn Đại Bi tự - 崇嚴事雲磊山大悲寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Ho%C3%A0ng-Qu%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-85VnaYJLPPe65KT695BD2A">Tặng Hoàng Quân Khâm kỳ 2 - 贈黃君欽其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/author-tWIJ_JcBg9FILAgkriOf3g">Huỳnh Thúc Kháng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/T%E1%BB%8B-d%E1%BB%8Bch-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-Igl2nlyKtjtFxMHuTfyvFQ">Tị dịch nhàn cư cảm tác kỳ 4 - 避疫閒居感作其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Vi%E1%BB%87n/To%E1%BA%A1-th%E1%BA%A1ch-minh/poem-LvAIPeNKA5xF-9ycVsrvjw">Toạ thạch minh - 座右銘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Vi%E1%BB%87n/author-j-BevTHvR1oyXw66IODG8A">Thôi Viện</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%E1%BA%BF-y%E1%BA%BFn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-93-OV94G2z33TdoBuUwa_A">Tuế yến hành - 歲晏行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%A9-t%E1%BB%AD-Hoan-h%E1%BB%99i-th%C3%AD-tr%C3%BAng-ph%C3%B3-b%E1%BA%A3ng/poem-xRbuuoTSWkEL4ivSEJfXSQ">Tứ tử Hoan hội thí trúng phó bảng - 賜子懽會試中副榜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gi%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AD-phu-th%C3%AA/poem-nvWXldPQFCgPzVvH2hpTWw">Vương giải tử phu thê - 王解子夫婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/author-WRSP543j56aeSlO4dZfsBQ">Ngô Gia Kỷ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
